%20Stock%20Exchange.%20That%20makes%20more%20sense%2C%20I%20thought%20%E2%80%94%20but%20also%2C%20only%20slightly%3F%20I%20thought%20the%20stock%20exchange%20guys%20were%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20serious%20ones%20in%20the%20room%2C%20helping%20companies%20grow%20and%20people%20save%20for%20retirement%2C%20not%20teaming%20up%20with%20the%20guys%20who%20let%20you%20guess%20when%20the%20US%20government%20will%20admit%20aliens%20exist.%20But%20thus%20is%20reality%20in%20the%20year%20of%20our%20Lord%202025%3A%20Americans%20have%20a%20growing%20appetite%20for%20leaving%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-betting-odds-gambling-lines-memecoins-prediction-markets-polymarket-stocks-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efortunes%20to%20the%20fates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20businesses%20are%20eager%20to%20capitalize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20are%20given%20the%20means%20to%20bet%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20bet%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Jordan%20Bender%2C%20an%20equity%20research%20analyst%20at%20Citizens%20JMP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20modern%20explosion%20of%20gambling%20in%20America%20began%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%202018%20decision%20to%20strike%20down%20a%20federal%20law%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-betting-apps-online-gambling-lottery-draftkings-fanduel-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprohibiting%20sports%20betting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leading%20to%20its%20proliferation%20across%20dozens%20of%20states.%20Now%2C%20much%20of%20the%20conversation%20is%20being%20dominated%20by%20another%20type%20of%20wagering%3A%20prediction%20markets.%20These%20platforms%2C%20which%20allow%20people%20to%20put%20money%20on%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20outcomes%2C%20from%20election%20results%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpolymarket-takes-bets-palisades-california-wildfire-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20disasters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20long%20been%20limited%20in%20the%20US.%20But%20recently%2C%20they've%20taken%20advantage%20of%20lax%20federal%20regulators%20and%20what%20they%20say%20are%20legal%20loopholes%20to%20offer%20their%20services%20in%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20definitely%20looks%2C%20smells%2C%20and%20feels%20like%20gambling%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Steve%20Ruddock%2C%20a%20gambling-industry%20analyst%20and%20consultant%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstraighttothepoint.substack.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStraight%20to%20the%20Point%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20newsletter%20about%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20these%20days.%20The%20lines%20between%20gambling%20and%20investing%20are%20increasingly%20blurred%2C%20from%20the%20crypto%20market%20to%20the%20stock%20market%20to%20sports%2C%20and%2C%20increasingly%2C%20everyday%20events.%20Arguments%20that%20this%20type%20of%20activity%20is%20beneficial%20because%20it%20shows%20us%20something%20about%20the%20wisdom%20of%20crowds%2C%20market%20inefficiencies%2C%20price%20discovery%2C%20or%20capital%20allocation%20are%20becoming%20harder%20and%20harder%20to%20buy.%20And%20businesses%2C%20even%20stodgy%20incumbents%20and%20unexpected%20players%2C%20are%20increasingly%20willing%20to%20capitalize%20on%20Americans'%20urge%20to%20risk%20their%20hard-earned%20cash.%20Everything's%20casino%2C%20and%20you're%20either%20getting%20in%20on%20the%20action%20or%20getting%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20a%20lot%20about%20a%20conversation%20I%20had%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20with%20Chris%20Grove%2C%20a%20sports-gambling-industry%20investor%20at%20Acies%20Investments%2C%20about%20the%20growth%20of%20sports%20betting%20apps%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquant-trading-susquehanna-sports-betting-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDraftKings%20and%20FanDuel%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20made%20a%20point%20that%20I%20discounted%20at%20the%20time%3A%20Once%20people%20get%20a%20taste%20for%20betting%20on%20one%20thing%2C%20they'll%20bet%20on%20a%20lot%20of%20things.%20This%20kind%20of%20gateway%20gambling%20represented%20a%20major%20opportunity%20not%20only%20for%20sportsbooks%20but%20also%20for%20investing%20apps%20and%20cryptocurrency%20platforms.%20When%20I%20relayed%20this%20to%20people%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20wearing%20a%20paranoid%20little%20tinfoil%20hat%2C%20but%20that%20case%20has%20quite%20clearly%20borne%20out%20in%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20hotspot%20has%20been%20prediction%20markets%2C%20most%20notably%20Kalshi%20and%20Polymarket%2C%20which%20match%20users%20willing%20to%20wager%20on%20either%20side%20of%20a%20discrete%20event.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshis-sports-predictions-come-under-fire-amid-march-madness-trades-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKalshi%20has%20made%20%3C%2Fa%3Ea%20major%20push%20into%20sports%2C%20including%20in%20states%20such%20as%20California%20and%20Texas%2C%20where%20traditional%20sports%20betting%20is%20illegal.%20And%20as%20part%20of%20its%20push%20to%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20super%20app%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobinhood-ceo-vlad-tenev-prediction-markets-election-future-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvesting%20platform%20Robinhood%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20started%20branching%20into%20betting%20markets%20in%20partnership%20with%20Kalshi.%20ICE%20has%20invested%20in%20Polymarket%20and%20will%20distribute%20the%20prediction%20market's%20data%20to%20investing%20customers%20trying%20to%20gauge%20sentiment%20on%20issues%20such%20as%20politics%2C%20business%20developments%2C%20and%20current%20events.%20Polymarket%2C%20once%20blocked%20for%20users%20in%20the%20US%2C%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20becoming%20available%20nationwide.%20The%20NHL%20has%20signed%20licensing%20agreements%20with%20both%20Kalshi%20and%20Polymarket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20traditional%20sportsbooks%2C%20which%20set%20the%20odds%20and%20against%20which%20gamblers%20bet%2C%20aren't%20only%20expanding%20their%20offerings%20with%20things%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdraftkings-models-online-casino-app-netflix-expands-original-games-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonline%20casino%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they're%20also%20taking%20a%20page%20out%20of%20their%20new%20competitors'%20book%2C%20too.%20FanDuel%20is%20partnering%20with%20CME%20Group%2C%20a%20derivatives%20marketplace%2C%20to%20build%20an%20events%20contracts%20platform%20in%20the%20US%20that%20will%20let%20customers%20put%20money%20on%20where%20the%20price%20of%20gold%20and%20oil%20are%20headed%2C%20as%20well%20as%20economic%20indicators%20such%20as%20GDP%20and%20inflation.%20DraftKings%20has%20acquired%20the%20predictions%20platform%20Railbird.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20reached%20for%20comment%2C%20a%20FanDuel%20spokesperson%20pointed%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmegroup.com%2Fmedia-room%2Fpress-releases%2F2025%2F8%2F20%2Fcme_group_and_fanduelpartnertodevelopinnovativeeventcontractspla.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20CME%20deal.%20DraftKings%20pointed%20to%20comments%20its%20CEO%2C%20Jason%20Robins%2C%20made%20at%20a%20gaming%20conference%20in%20October%2C%20downplaying%20concerns%20about%20competition%20from%20prediction%20markets%2C%20saying%20that%20sports%20betting%20apps%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bvastly%20superior%20experience.%26quot%3B%20Polymarket%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20head%20is%20spinning%20at%20all%20of%20this%2C%20it's%20understandable%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20all%20fast-moving%20and%20precarious.%20For%20one%20thing%2C%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20reversal%20of%20previous%20regulatory%20approaches.%20Gambling%20has%20historically%20been%20regulated%20by%20states%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20matter%20now%20is%20whether%20prediction%20markets%20are%20considered%20gambling%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20whether%20states%20should%20regulate%20them.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-gambling-conference-next-summit-takeaways-ai-predictions-sweepstakes-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrediction%20markets%20say%20they're%20OK%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20they're%20simply%20offering%20contracts%20on%20the%20outcomes%20of%20future%20events%20and%20aren't%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20trade.%20Since%20these%20are%20futures%20contracts%2C%20like%20those%20offered%20for%20gold%20or%20oil%2C%20the%20theory%20%E2%80%94%20and%20current%20reality%20%E2%80%94%20is%20that%20prediction%20markets%20should%20be%20federally%20regulated%20by%20the%20Commodity%20Futures%20Trading%20Commission%2C%20not%20by%20individual%20states.%20The%20CFTC%20may%20be%20going%20along%20with%20this%20for%20the%20time%20being%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20gray%20area.%20Basically%2C%20an%2018-year-old%20in%20California%20can%20bet%20on%20a%20Dodgers%20game%20on%20Kalshi%20now%2C%20if%20it's%20considered%20a%20federally-regulated%20event%20contract.%20If%20it's%20sports%20gambling%2C%20that's%20illegal%20in%20California%2C%20and%20even%20if%20it%20were%20allowed%2C%20most%20states%20put%20the%20age%20limit%20at%2021.%20Sportsbooks%20have%20state%20tax%20obligations%20that%20prediction%20markets%20avoid.%20Winnings%20are%20taxed%20differently%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20vast%20majority%20of%20people%20that%20I%20deal%20with%20in%20this%20industry%20look%20at%20this%20and%20say%2C%20'This%20is%20gambling%2C%20it's%20insane%20that%20we're%20having%20this%20conversation%2C'%26quot%3B%20Citizens%20JMP's%20Bender%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20states%2C%20including%20Massachusetts%20and%20Nevada%2C%20have%20sued%20or%20sent%20cease-and-desist%20letters%20to%20prediction%20markets%2C%20alleging%20they're%20offering%20illegal%20sports%20gambling.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-rise-of-the-native-american-casino-2013-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENative%20American%20tribes%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20operate%20casinos%20and%20sports%20betting%20operations%20in%20certain%20states%20have%20made%20similar%20claims.%20The%20answer%20to%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20is%20all%20of%20this%20activity%20on%20prediction%20markets%20kosher%3F%26quot%3B%20seems%20to%20be%20%C2%AF%5C%5C_(%E3%83%84)_%2F%C2%AF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%20question%20is%2C%20do%20these%20contracts%20violate%20all%20of%20the%20sports%20betting%20regulations%3F%20And%20that's%20kind%20of%20where%20things%20are%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Chad%20Beynon%2C%20an%20equity%20analyst%20at%20Macquarie.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20tricky%20investing%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20in%20this%20space%20right%20now%2C%20because%20it%20might%20completely%20go%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20emailed%20statement%2C%20a%20Kalshi%20spokesperson%20told%20me%20the%20company%20is%20%26quot%3Bconfident%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20legal%20standing.%20%26quot%3BFederal%20and%20state%20turf%20wars%20over%20commodities%20markets%20have%20been%20going%20on%20for%20decades%20in%20America%2C%20and%20the%20law%20is%20clear%20%E2%80%94%20Kalshi%20exists%20under%20the%20sole%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20CFTC.%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20trickiness%20hasn't%20stopped%20some%20major%20players%20from%20getting%20involved.%20Peter%20Thiel's%20Founders%20Fund%20has%20invested%20in%20Polymarket.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpolymarket-sees-valuation-skyrocket-in-new-funding-round-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%20Jr.%20is%20involved%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20both%20Kalshi%20and%20Polymarket.%20The%20president's%20social%20media%20company%2C%20Trump%20Media%2C%20is%20planning%20to%20allow%20its%20Truth%20Social%20users%20to%20jump%20into%20prediction%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20look%20at%20the%20money%20that%20is%20lined%20up%20behind%20these%20two%20names%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20money%20that%20has%20historically%20been%20involved%20with%20regulated%20gambling%2C%26quot%3B%20Grove%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20what%20counts%20as%20gambling%20has%20always%20been%20hazy%20to%20define%2C%20says%20Peter%20Malyshev%2C%20a%20partner%20in%20the%20financial%20services%20group%20at%20Cadwalader%2C%20Wickersham%20%26amp%3B%20Taft.%20What%20constitutes%20a%20legitimate%20commodity%20futures%20contract%20is%20something%20regulators%20and%20courts%20battled%20over%20in%20the%2019th%20and%20early%2020th%20centuries%2C%20and%20when%20they%20arrived%20at%20their%20current%20definition%2C%20they%20couldn't%20have%20envisioned%20a%20world%20of%20sports%20betting%20taking%20place%20on%20mobile%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20notion%20of%20what%20gambling%20is%2C%20what%20is%20not%2C%20is%20very%2C%20very%20loosey%20goosey%20and%20it's%20arbitrary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20almost%20astounding%20to%20think%20about%20how%20commonplace%20speculation%20has%20become%20across%20the%20economy.%20A%20survey%20by%20the%20American%20Gaming%20Association%20found%20that%2055%25%20of%20US%20adults%20gambled%20in%202024%2C%20and%20Americans%20bet%20almost%20%24150%20billion%20on%20sports%20alone.%20That%20doesn't%20include%20activities%20that%20very%20much%20resemble%20gambling%2C%20such%20as%20exotic%20stock%20options%2C%20crypto%2C%20and%20prediction%20markets.%20I%20recently%20discovered%20members%20of%20my%20family%20are%20crossing%20the%20Wisconsin-Illinois%20border%20to%20place%20sports%20bets%20on%20NFL%20Sundays%2C%20as%20gambling%20is%20legal%20in%20the%20latter%20state%20but%20not%20the%20former.%20And%20I%20have%20not%20been%20immune%20to%20the%20allure.%20On%20a%20recent%20trip%20to%20Chicago%2C%20I%20stopped%20at%20a%20DraftKings%20bar%20outside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-all-30-mlb-stadiums-look-like-from-space-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWrigley%20Field%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20I%20could%20place%20bets.%20During%20a%20pre-season%20Bulls%20game%2C%20I%20checked%20out%20a%20FanDuel%20lounge%20to%20catch%20some%20contemporaneous%20baseball%20and%20hockey%20games%20and%20placed%20a%20few%20small%20bets%20from%20my%20phone.%20This%20is%20all%20stuff%20that%20would%20have%20been%20unimaginable%20five%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20upon%20a%20time%2C%20you%20had%20to%20know%20a%20bookie%20or%20a%20broker%20or%20go%20to%20a%20casino%2C%20that's%20a%20lot%20more%20steps%2C%20and%20now%20it's%20just%20a%20few%20taps%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Parker%20Bach%2C%20a%20Ph.D.%20student%20at%20the%20University%20of%20North%20Carolina-Chapel%20Hill%2C%20who%20is%20studying%20digital%20political%20culture%20and%20prediction%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20less-than-ideal%20possible%20outcomes%20of%20gambling's%20expansion%20were%20put%20on%20full%20display%20in%20recent%20days%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-betting-scandal-college-athletes-ncaa-nba-terry-rozier-billups-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENBA%20betting%20scandal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Federal%20prosecutors%20allege%20that%20current%20and%20former%20basketball%20players%2C%20as%20well%20as%20people%20in%20their%20orbit%2C%20passed%20along%20insider%20information%20about%20players%20ahead%20of%20games%20to%20place%20bets%20on%20them.%20Sportsbooks%20are%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20alleged%20crimes%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20the%20ones%20that%20were%20defrauded.%20However%2C%20the%20case%20has%20made%20clear%20opportunities%20for%20funny%20businesses%20that%20widespread%20gambling%20affords.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-betting-debt-bankruptcy-gambling-young-men-research-addiction-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EConsumer%20protection%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20legal%20issues%20aside%2C%20it's%20worth%20considering%20how%20some%20of%20this%20activity%20is%20distorting%20the%20economy%20and%20blurring%20the%20lines%20between%20investing%20and%20pure%20speculation.%20Investing%20is%20intended%20to%20drive%20capital%20allocation%20in%20ways%20that%20foster%20good%20businesses%2C%20good%20services%2C%20and%20good%20products%2C%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20grow%20the%20economy.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdraftkings-responsible-gaming-chief-on-gambling-reputation-problem-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGambling%20is%20entertainment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20when%20money%20from%20the%20former%20pot%20goes%20into%20the%20latter%20pot%2C%20that%20could%20become%20a%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20capital%20that's%20going%20toward%20creating%20anything%2C%20it's%20just%20a%20transfer%20of%20wealth.%20Tyler%20Gellasch%2C%20the%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20Healthy%20Markets%20Association%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20focused%20on%20increasing%20transparency%20for%20investors%2C%20says%20that%20the%20drive%20to%20funnel%20more%20money%20into%20speculative%20activities%20isn't%20just%20a%20concern%20for%20individual%20bettors%20or%20investors.%20%26quot%3BIt%20also%20takes%20real%20money%20out%20of%20the%20real%20economy%20and%20into%20essentially%20side%20bets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tells%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProponents%20of%20prediction%20markets%20say%20they%20have%20real%20value.%20They%20tap%20into%20the%20%26quot%3Bwisdom%20of%20the%20crowd%26quot%3B%20and%2C%20in%20elections%2C%20may%20rival%20polling%20in%20predicting%20who%20will%20come%20out%20ahead.%20They%20can%20be%20used%20as%20a%20hedge%20against%20the%20possibility%20of%20different%20events%20%E2%80%94%20you%20place%20a%20little%20money%20on%20something%20that%20would%20hurt%20you%2C%20li