igcaption%3EJoakim%20Sj%C3%B6blom%20has%20raised%20initial%20money%20for%20an%20ambitious%20project%3A%20Building%20a%20new%20TNT%20factory%20in%20Western%20Europe.%3Cp%3E%C3%85sa%20Sj%C3%B6str%C3%B6m%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20fintech%20entrepreneur%20has%20a%20bold%20ambition%20to%20build%20a%20TNT%20plant%20in%20Sweden.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETNT%20is%20essential%20for%20many%20types%20of%20ammo%2C%20but%20Europe%20has%20only%20one%20factory%20that%20makes%20it%2C%20in%20Poland.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESwebal%20aims%20to%20produce%204%2C500%20tons%20of%20TNT%20annually%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Scandinavia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20minutes%20west%20of%20the%20Swedish%20town%20of%20Nora%2C%20there's%20a%20quiet%20patch%20of%20forest%20behind%20a%20cluster%20of%20summer%20homes%2C%20sitting%20by%20a%20lake%20where%20the%20morning%20mist%20rises%20just%20in%20time%20to%20catch%20the%20sun's%20glow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20where%20Joakim%20Sj%C3%B6blom%20aims%20to%20build%20a%20new%20factory%20for%20one%20of%20armsmaking's%20most%20dangerous%20processes%20%E2%80%94%20manufacturing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-finally-moving-produce-key-explosive-tnt-at-home-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrinitrotoluene%2C%20or%20TNT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20NATO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20daughter%20turned%20one%20month%20old%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20startup%20CEO%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20mid-October.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20was%20one%20of%20the%20key%20reasons%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20this%3A%20if%20I%20can%20contribute%20to%20making%20sure%20that%20they%20do%20not%20experience%20a%20conflict%20growing%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20site%20of%20his%20factory-to-be%20is%20serviced%20by%20an%20old%20railroad%20track%2C%20where%2080-foot-tall%20trees%20will%20soon%20make%20way%20for%20chemical%20tanks%2C%20reactors%2C%20and%20a%20pump%20tower%20that%20peeks%20over%20the