%20chokepoint%20in%20a%20major%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20been%20a%20political%20decision%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurope-shifting-strategy-boost-ukraine-weapons-defense-production-russia-war-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshift%20manufacturing%20back%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Sj%C3%B6blom%20said%20of%20general%20attitudes%20in%20Europe.%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20an%20incident%20where%20we%20need%20to%20close%20the%20borders%2C%20we%20should%20be%20able%20to%20maintain%20production.%20We%20should%20not%20have%20an%20import%20dependency%20on%20critical%20raw%20material.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cee3a199-887f-4525-b1ad-cf46f4be936e%5C%22%3EEurope's%20rush%20to%20fix%20its%20supply%20chain%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20howitzer%20fires%20a%20shell%20in%20Western%20Ukraine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6909a011c007ca8c27382d02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20NATO%20howitzer%2C%20the%20bread%20and%20butter%20of%20artillery%2C%20relies%20on%20155mm%20shells%2C%20which%20need%20TNT.%3Cp%3EOksana%20Parafeniuk%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESj%C3%B6blom%20founded%20Sweden%20Ballistics%20AB%2C%20or%20Swebal%2C%20in%202024%20after%20selling%20his%20fintech%20firm%2C%20Minna%20Technologies%2C%20to%20Mastercard%20in%20the%20same%20year.%20That%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsweden-exactly-what-west-nato-needs-to-counter-putin-russia-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESweden%20also%20joined%20NATO.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwebal%20submitted%20an%20environmental%20permit%20this%20year%20to%20produce%20an%20annual%20capacity%20of%204%2C500%20metric%20tons%20of%20TNT%2C%20or%20enough%20for%20roughly%20450%2C000%20of%20the%20artillery%20shells%20that%20NATO%20desperately%20wants%20to%20surge%20production%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Swedish%20firm%20expects%20to%20break%20ground%20early%20next%20year%20and%20begin%20production%20by%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup's%20big%20draw%20is%20its%20European%20supply%20chain%2C%20Sj%C3%B6blom%20said.%20Swebal%20plans%20to%20source%20100%25%20of%20its%20raw%20material%20from%20Sweden%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-baltic-sea-patrol-driving-down-undersea-sabotage-western-officials-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20Baltic%20Sea%20area%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELukas%20Bauer%2C%20an%20expert%20in%20energetics%20such%20as%20TNT%20at%20the%20Ludwig-Maximilian%20University%20of%20Munich%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it's%20generally%20quite%20easy%20to%20find%20the%20materials%20needed%20to%20make%20TNT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20those%20chemicals%20are%20relatively%20inexpensive%20and%20can%20be%20obtained%20in%20large%20amounts%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bauer%2C%20who%20is%20not%20involved%20with%20Swebal's%20project%2C%20adding%20that%20producing%20TNT%20generally%20costs%20below%20%2420%20per%20kilogram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESourcing%20isn't%20usually%20the%20main%20concern.%20The%20process%20for%20making%20NATO-standard%20TNT%20is%20highly%20toxic%2C%20and%20while%20the%20final%20product%20is%20generally%20quite%20stable%2C%20manufacturing%20it%20comes%20with%20a%20greater%20risk%20of%20accidental%20detonation.%20That's%20partially%20why%20the%20West%20was%20content%20to%20leave%20manufacturing%20to%20Asia%20after%20the%20Cold%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Ukrainian%20serviceman%20picks%20up%20a%20155mm%20artillery%20shell.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69099e57c007ca8c27382cf3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20chewed%20through%20much%20of%20Europe's%20155mm%20shell%20supply%2C%20and%20NATO%20member%20states%20there%20are%20concerned%20they%20can't%20rearm%20in%20time.%3Cp%3ERoman%20Chop%2FGlobal%20Images%20Ukraine%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EProducing%20TNT%20in%20Europe%20is%20also%20more%20expensive%2C%20but%20it%20falls%20neatly%20in%20line%20with%20the%20European%20Union's%20new%20requirements%20for%20arms%20makers.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20bloc%20set%20a%20target%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Fcommission%2Fpresscorner%2Fdetail%2Fen%2Fip_24_1321%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E60%25%20of%20its%20defense%20procurement%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20sourced%20internally%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20policy%20shift%2C%20Sj%C3%B6blom%20and%20his%20cofounder%2C%20engineer%20Carl%20Duforce%2C%20are%20just%20one%20of%20several%20new%20Western%20players%20breaking%20into%20the%20TNT%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinland's%20government%20announced%20in%20January%20that%20it%20is%20building%20a%20TNT%20plant%2C%20with%20construction%20scheduled%20for%20completion%20by%202028.%20Work%20is%20also%20underway%20to%20restart%20production%20at%20a%20Czech-Greek%20TNT%20factory%20in%20a%20town%20in%20the%20greater%20Athens%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20pond%2C%20the%20US%20Army%20has%20assigned%20Repkon%20USA%20the%20task%20of%20producing%20TNT%20at%20a%20new%20plant%20in%20Kentucky%20by%20November%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20surge%20in%20demand%20is%20fueled%20by%20a%20sense%20of%20urgency%20in%20the%20West%20to%20drastically%20increase%20ammunition%20production.%20NATO%20warned%20in%20June%20that%20Russia%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-ammunition-production-nato-mark-rutte-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eproducing%20roughly%20four%20times%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20many%20artillery%20shells%20as%20the%20entire%20Western%20alliance%2C%20despite%20its%2025-times%20smaller%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESj%C3%B6blom%20said%20the%20TNT%20market%20isn't%20even%20coming%20close%20to%20meeting%20the%20West's%20needs%20for%20now%2C%20and%20is%20confident%20that%20Swebal's%20annual%20capacity%20of%204%2C500%20tons%20will%20be%20in%20hot%20demand%20for%20at%20least%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20all%20of%20these%20ongoing%20projects%20are%20realized%2C%20we're%20not%20even%20halfway%20to%20matching%20what%20Russia%20can%20produce%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eaace005-6b72-4042-baeb-4403ccab9e7d%5C%22%3EMaking%20TNT%20in%20a%20post-Cold%20War%20Europe%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESwebal%20is%20now%20waiting%20for%20a%20final%20go-ahead%20from%20the%20Swedish%20court%20of%20environment%2C%20which%20the%20firm%20expects%20to%20receive%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegulatory%20requirements%20in%20Sweden%20are%20stringent%20for%20this%20type%20of%20factory%2C%20even%20with%20the%20nation%20now%20favoring%20a%20defense%20buildup.%20Swebal%20spent%20the%20better%20part%20of%20two%20years%20conducting%2014%20studies%20on%20its%20site%20for%20environmental%20approval%2C%20checking%20for%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalredlist.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotected%20animal%20species%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eancient%20remains%2C%20and%20other%20elements%20that%20would%20rule%20out%20the%20area%20for%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwebal's%20factory%2C%20including%20its%20parking%20lot%2C%20would%20span%20three%20acres%2C%20but%20the%20company%20also%20has%20an%20agreement%20option%20to%20purchase%20about%2060%20acres%20of%20the%20surrounding%20forest%20as%20a%20contingency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22TNT%20Factory%20construction%20site%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6908fbf4c007ca8c27382300%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoughly%20three%20acres%20of%20pine%20and%20birch%20will%20be%20cut%20down%20in%20this%20production%20forest%20to%20make%20way%20for%20the%20TNT%20factory.%3Cp%3E%C3%85sa%20Sj%C3%B6str%C3%B6m%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20buying%20a%20lot%20bigger%2C%20basically%20to%20make%20sure%20in%20the%20future%20that%20we%20don't%20have%20neighbors%20close%20by%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sebastian%20Reismer%2C%20the%20company's%20construction%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20permit%20allows%20it%20to%20store%20up%20to%2025%20tons%20of%20TNT%20on-site%20at%20a%20time%2C%20and%20it%20has%20to%20prepare%20for%20contingencies%20in%20the%20event%20of%20an%20explosion.%20The%20surrounding%20forest%20could%20help%20to%20mitigate%20the%20shock%20wave%20and%20shrapnel%20from%20an%20accidental%20blast%2C%20as%20well%20as%20soften%20noise%20pollution%20from%20factory%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20we%20are%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Duforce%2C%20Swebal's%20cofounder%20and%20COO%2C%20said%20of%20the%20forest%20near%20Nora.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20around%20700%20meters%20to%20one%20kilometer%20away%20from%20the%20closest%20civil%20object%2C%20like%20a%20house%20or%20a%20main%20road.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20facility%20itself%20is%20designed%20to%20include%20about%20a%20dozen%20acid%20tanks%20connected%20to%20a%2090-foot%20tower%20for%20concentrating%20the%20raw%20material%20within.%20At%20the%20core%20of%20the%20factory%2C%20these%20chemicals%20are%20pumped%20for%20processing%20into%20TNT%20inside%20a%204%2C300-square-foot%20compound%20encircled%20by%20a%20set%20of%20thick%2C%2020-foot-tall%20earthen%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwebal%20plans%20to%20enforce%20the%20surrounding%20three-acre%20perimeter%20with%20electric%20and%20barbed%20wire%2C%20surveillance%20cameras%2C%20and%20a%2024%2F7%20security%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ebf13ce-49eb-4f1a-ae10-9765f38c1be4%5C%22%3EA%20dangerous%2C%20toxic%20process%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Founders%3A%20Sj%C3%B6blom%2C%20Duforce%2C%20and%20Reismer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6908fa52599d46a4ccc15a90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDuforce%2C%20Sj%C3%B6blom%2C%20and%20Reismer%20are%20coordinating%20roughly%2050%20consultants%20and%20contractors%20while%20moving%20toward%20construction.%3Cp%3E%C3%85sa%20Sj%C3%B6str%C3%B6m%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESj%C3%B6blom%2C%20Duforce%2C%20and%20Reismer%20are%20currently%20Swebal's%20only%20employees%2C%20but%20the%20startup%20aims%20to%20hire%20about%2050%20Swedish%20full-timers%20when%20its%20factory%20is%20complete.%20For%20now%2C%20it%20works%20with%20several%20dozen%20consultants%20and%20contractors%20while%20preparing%20for%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwebal%20estimates%20that%20it%20will%20need%20about%2080%20million%20to%2090%20million%20euros%2C%20or%20%2493%20million%20to%20%24104%20million%2C%20to%20build%20the%20TNT%20factory.%20The%20firm%20announced%20in%20June%20that%20it%20raised%20%243.5%20million%20from%20investors%20such%20as%20Thomas%20von%20Koch%2C%20a%20former%20managing%20partner%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feqt-using-chatgpt-artificial-intelligence-boost-vc-pe-businesses-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEQT%20Partners.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESj%C3%B6blom%20said%20his%20team%20will%20pursue%20a%20%26quot%3Bsubstantially%20bigger%26quot%3B%20funding%20round%20once%20it%20receives%20its%20final%20permits.%20While%20he%20said%20demand%20for%20TNT%20is%20high%2C%20he%20also%20acknowledged%20he's%20embarking%20on%20a%20risky%20endeavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20risk%20appetite%2C%20as%20a%20startup%2C%20is%20sky-high%20because%20we've%20got%20nothing%20to%20lose%2C%26quot%3B%20Sj%C3%B6blom%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaking%20TNT%20involves%20repeatedly%20mixing%20the%20chemical%20toluene%20with%20concentrated%20sulfuric%20and%20nitric%20acid%2C%20which%20are%20corrosive%20and%20can%20release%20toxic%20fumes.%20This%20process%20generates%20a%20lot%20of%20heat%2C%20which%2C%20if%20not%20controlled%2C%20can%20cause%20a%20detonation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20reasons%2C%20Swebal%20plans%20to%20have%20only%20two%20rooms%20where%20human%20workers%20are%20regularly%20present%20at%20the%20factory%20%E2%80%94%20a%20laboratory%20for%20final%20product%20testing%20and%20a%20fortified%20control%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3EOur%20vision%20is%20to%20make%20this%20completely%20automated%2C%26quot%3B%20Sj%C3%B6blom%20said%20of%20the%20manufacturing%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20issue%20of%20waste.%20Purifying%20TNT%20to%20NATO%20standards%20creates%20a%20byproduct%20called%20redwater%2C%20which%20Bauer%2C%20the%20energetics%20expert%2C%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Btoxic%2C%20carcinogenic%2C%20mutagenic%20wastewater.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20companies%20dumped%20redwater%20into%20waterways%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20now%20usually%20store%20it%20in%20basins%20to%20be%20incinerated%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESj%C3%B6blom%20said%20Swebal%20will%20truck%20its%20redwater%20to%20a%20third-party%20waste%20management%20company%20that%20is%20a%2045-minute%20drive%20from%20the%20factory%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20have%20any%20destruction%20on-site%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20wastewater.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22db1d1753-a9e0-4f30-95b0-6a19e752aa20%5C%22%3ENot%20in%20my%20backyard%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227102%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Duforce%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6908fb59c007ca8c273822de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDuforce%2C%20an%20engineer%20and%20Sj%C3%B6blom's%20neighbor%2C%20moved%20to%20Nora%20to%20help%20with%20community%20engagement%20for%20the%20TNT%20factory.%3Cp%3E%C3%85sa%20Sj%C3%B6str%C3%B6m%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Duforce%20has%20been%20living%20in%20the%20nearby%20town%20of%20Nora%20since%20February%20to%20speak%20to%20residents.%20Some%20are%20not%20thrilled%20to%20have%20a%20new%20TNT%20factory%20near%20their%20summer%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExpecting%20to%20soon%20be%20the%20area's%20second-largest%20employer%2C%20Swebal%20is%20already%20sponsoring%20the%20neighborhood%20tennis%20and%20padel%20clubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20local%20region%20is%20also%20familiar%20with%20the%20arms%20industry.%20Swebal's%20new%20facility%20is%20built%20along%20Sweden's%20%26quot%3Bmilitary%20belt.%26quot%3B%20Across%20the%20lake%20from%20the%20TNT%20factory%20sits%20an%20old%20dynamite%20plant%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanhattan-project-scientists-who-won-nobel-prizes-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAlfred%20Nobel%3C%2Fa%3E's%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwebal's%20factory%20will%20rely%20on%20about%20nine%20trucks%20a%20day%20to%20deliver%20its%20material%2C%20and%20so%20it%20must%20build%20a%20road%20leading%20into%20and%20out%20of%20its%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESj%C3%B6blom%20said%20the%20notion%20of%20increased%20traffic%20has%20upset%20some%20nearby%20residents%2C%20but%20he%20believes%20Europe%20must%20build%20an%20arsenal%20to%20deter%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20not%20happy%20that%20there%20will%20be%20trucks%20going%20by%2C%20and%20they're%20not%20happy%20about%20the%20trees%20coming%20down%2C%20and%2C%20you%20know%2C%20there%20will%20not%20be%20as%20many%20squirrels%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20as%20he%20walked%20the%20abandoned%20railway%2C%20under%20the%20shade%20of%20towering%20forest.%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20if%20a%20war%20happens%2C%20maybe%20there%20will%20be%20no%20more%20trees.%20There%20won't%20be%20any%20squirrels%20left.%26quot%3B%3C%2F