3Cfigcaption%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20name-dropped%20six%20startups%20playing%20in%20the%20AI%20agent%20space.%3Cp%3Epicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20has%20dialed%20up%20his%20warning%20that%20the%20US%20is%20falling%20behind%20China%20in%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20Beijing's%20subsidies%20are%20supercharging%20its%20tech%20firms%20while%20US%20rules%20pile%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWashington%20has%20banned%20sales%20of%20Nvidia's%20most%20advanced%20AI%20chips%20to%20China.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20has%20intensified%20his%20warnings%20about%20the%20United%20States%20falling%20behind%20China%20in%20the%20race%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fartificial-intelligence%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20dominance%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20saying%20the%20East%20Asian%20nation%20could%20soon%20pull%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20is%20going%20to%20win%20the%20AI%20race%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20told%20the%20Financial%20Times%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20media%20outlet's%20Future%20of%20AI%20Summit%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20blunt%20remarks%20underscored%20the%20shrinking%20technological%20gap%20between%20the%20world's%20two%20largest%20economies%2C%20locked%20in%20both%20a%20trade%20war%20and%20a%20battle%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20supremacy.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20told%20the%20FT%20that%20%26quot%3Bcynicism%26quot%3B%20is%20holding%20the%20West%20back%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20it%20needs%20%26quot%3Bmore%20optimism%26quot%3B%20to%20compete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20a%20growing%20wave%20of%20AI%20regulations%20emerging%20across%20US%20states%2C%20warning%20that%20too%20many%20new%20rules%20could%20stifle%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20contr