AA%20Administrator%20Bryan%20Bedford%20said%20the%20agency%20would%20be%20working%20with%20airlines%20to%20determine%20how%20the%20flight%20reduction%20would%20be%20implemented.%20He%20said%20if%20there%20are%20additional%20staffing%20issues%2C%20additional%20measures%20would%20be%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20data%20is%20telling%20us%20we%20need%20to%20do%20more%2C%20and%20we%20are%20going%20to%20do%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20the%20press%20conference.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20reassure%20the%20American%20travelers%20that%20it%20is%20absolutely%20safe%20to%20fly%20in%20the%20American%20skies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBedford%20also%20said%20that%2C%20in%20his%2035%20years%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20he%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20a%20similar%20measure%20ever%20being%20taken%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20new%20territory%26quot%3B%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongest-government-shutdown-ever-impact-on-airports-snap-workforce-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egovernment%20shutdown%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shutdown%2C%20which%20has%20lasted%20for%2036%20days%2C%20is%20the%20longest%20in%20American%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20to%20reduce%20scheduled%20flight%20capacity%2C%20while%20necessary%20to%20keep%20our%20skies%20safe%2C%20will%20inevitably%20affect%20the%20travel%20experience%2C%20leading%20to%20fewer%20flights%2C%20longer%20delays%2C%20and%20more%20disruptions%20for%20travelers%2C%26quot%3B%20Geoff%20Freeman%2C%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthanksgiving-travel-chaos-companies-warn-government-shutdown-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20Travel%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20provided%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAll%20government%20shutdowns%20are%20irresponsible%2C%20and%20this%20decision%20underscores%20the%20urgent%20need%20to%20reopen%20the%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuffy%20reiterated%20that%20flying%20is%20still%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20aviation%20safety%20consultant%20Anthony%20Brickhouse%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20controllers%20are%20highly%20skilled%20individuals%2C%20but%20humans%20can%20be%20stretched%20too%20thin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20design%20systems%20to%20minimize%20the%20impact%20of%20human%20mistakes%2C%20but%20when%20we%20add%20financial%20stress%20and%20fatigue%20to%20an%20already%20high-stress%20job%2C%20we%20could%20be%20looking%20at%20something%20a%20lot%20more%20serious%20than%20a%20two%20or%20three-hour%20delay%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20emailed%20for%20comment%2C%20the%20FAA%20sent%20an%20auto-reply%20with%20the%20following%20statement%20on%20air%20traffic%20controller%20staffing%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20Secretary%20Duffy%20has%20said%2C%20there%20have%20been%20increased%20staffing%20shortages%20across%20the%20system.%20When%20that%20happens%2C%20the%20FAA%20slows%20traffic%20into%20some%20airports%20to%20ensure%20safe%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22abbcd800-9490-4127-8829-813d2daaa517%5C%22%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20what%20flights%20will%20be%20cut%2C%20but%20the%20impact%20could%20be%20significant%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESean%20Cudahy%2C%20an%20aviation%20reporter%20at%20The%20Points%20Guy%2C%20said%20because%20this%20will%20likely%20impact%2040%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-canada-biggest-airports-ranked-by-traveler-satisfaction-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebusiest%20airports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20include%20major%20airline%20hubs%2C%20%26quot%3Byou're%20going%20to%20feel%20this%20impact%20across%20the%20entire%20country%20because%20these%20are%20going%20to%20be%20hubs%20that%20have%20flights%20going%20to%20every%20city%20imaginable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20compiled%20by%20Cirium%2C%20the%20aviation%20analytics%20company%2C%20a%2010%25%20reduction%20in%20flights%20at%20the%2040%20busiest%20airports%20could%20result%20in%20as%20many%20as%201%2C800%20flights%20and%20268%2C000%20seats%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Chicago%20O'Hare%20International%20Airport%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20if%2010%25%20of%20flights%20on%20Friday%20are%20cut%2C%20that%20would%20impact%20121%20flights%20and%2014%2C524%20seats%2C%20according%20to%20Cirium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20have%20a%20flight%20this%20weekend%20or%20next%20week%2C%20I%20would%20definitely%20be%20concerned%20about%20whether%20that's%20going%20to%20take%20off%20and%20especially%20take%20off%20on%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Cudahy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECudahy%20said%20he%20expects%20more%20specific%20information%20to%20be%20released%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20but%20recommended%20that%20travelers%20keep%20up%20to%20date%20with%20their%20airlines%20and%20check%20their%20apps%20regularly%20for%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Akvlamis%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ekvlamis%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%40kelseyv.21%3Cem%3E.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffaa-cuts-flights-capacity-busiest-markets-safety-government-shutdown-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17623