20I%20was%20curious%20about%20how%20large%20companies%20scale%20and%20how%20their%20management%20methods%20drive%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20to%20innovate.%20I%20wanted%20to%20approach%20things%20from%20a%20market%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223970%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%20graduation%2C%20He%20Jiabin%20wanted%20to%20learn%20how%20large%20companies%20scale%20ideas%20and%20drive%20innovation.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69085f30599d46a4ccc1515c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222978%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20graduation%2C%20He%20wanted%20to%20learn%20how%20large%20companies%20scale%20ideas%20and%20drive%20innovation.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20He%20Jiabin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2294977b03-48fe-4bbc-934c-75a48b8b7ccc%5C%22%3EFrom%20Big%20Tech%20to%20startup%20builder%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduation%2C%20I%20joined%20Baidu's%20learning%20lab%20as%20an%20interface%20designer%2C%20working%20on%20smart%20bicycles%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftensor-startup-personally-owned-fully-autonomous-car-no-human-supervsion-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eself-driving%20cars%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20smart%20glasses%20before%20moving%20to%20its%20research%20institute.%20While%20autonomous%20driving%20succeeded%2C%20other%20promising%20projects%20weren't%20pursued.%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20products%20people%20could%20actually%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20joined%20the%20founding%20team%20of%20Ling%20Technology%2C%20which%20built%20Luka%20%E2%80%94%20an%20owl-shaped%20robot%20that%20reads%20to%20kids.%20We%20sold%204%20to%205%20million%20units.%20I%20was%20promoted%20to%20partner%2C%20overseeing%20product%2C%20design%2C%20production%2C%20and%20marketing.%20I%20stayed%20for%20five%20years%2C%20until%20intense%20competition%20drove%20down%20prices%2C%20and%20China's%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fw